he current management team and company strategy represent the best path for=
ward to maximize the long-term shareholder value.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The problem for Murray is that he absolutely c=
annot raise the $4 billion he needs to buy Getty unless Getty is willing to=
 talk to him, and Getty is not willing to talk to him unless he can credibl=
y promise to raise the $4 billion. Ah well.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The stock is up a bit today? It closed at $5.0=
